snippet.title: CHICKEN 65 IDLI | Fried Chicken Idli Recipe Cooking In Village | Idli Cooking with Chicken Recipe
snippet.description:
n this video, we bring you a unique and mouthwatering recipe, Chicken 65 Idli!  A fusion of South Indian tradition and spicy flavors, this dish combines soft, fluffy idlis with crispy, flavorful fried chicken. Watch as we prepare this innovative recipe in our beautiful village setting, using fresh ingredients and traditional cooking methods.

What’s special about this recipe?

The perfect blend of soft idlis and spicy Chicken 65.
Simple steps that you can follow to recreate this dish at home.
A wholesome and flavorful meal for all occasions!
Join us for this delicious adventure filled with authentic village vibes.

Sunn Mere Dil Episode 27 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream - Wahaj Ali - Maya Ali - 2nd January 2025 - Har Pal Geo

Sunn Mera Dil Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Haseeb Hasan
Writer: Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

snippet.description:
Experience the heartfelt emotions of '12 Varsh Juno Prem' by Rakesh Barot only on @SaregamaGujarati   🎶

રાકેશ બારોટના '12 વર્ષ જુનો પ્રેમ' ગીતનો અનુભવ કરો, ફક્ત @SaregamaGujarati  પર.

Credits:
Singer: Rakesh Barot
Producer: Red Velvet Cinema 
Artist: Rakesh Barot, Viyona Patil, Divya Vaniya 
Director: Pranav Jethva
Concept: Savya Bhati ,Pranv Jethva
Music: Mehul Barot
Lyrics: Naresh Thakor Vayad

Choreographer: Deepak Turi 
Editing: Om Miyani

Production: Satubha. Jigar Panchal 
Light: Kalpesh Jadav 
Spot: Raju and Akshay 
Rakesh Barot Costume: Manisha R Barot

Lyrics:
એ જમાનો હતો એ જબરો ને હું કરતોતો એને બહુ પ્યાર 
જતોર્યો જમાનો ને વરસ થઇ જ્યાં બાર 
એ સાયકલ ઉપર બેસી ને ભણવા જાતા અમે નેહાળ હારો હાર 
જતોર્યો જમાનો ને વરસ થઇ જ્યાં બાર 
હો આજ વાટ્યો જોવાંમાં ઓખો ના ખૂટ્યા નૂર
એની યાદો માં હું થઇ જ્યો ગોડો તુર
એ હેત ભર્યો હાથ મારે વિખૂટો પડ્યો અને જીવું થઇ ને લાચાર 
જતોર્યો જમાનો ને વરસ થઇ જ્યાં બાર 1
એ અડકો દડકો દહીં દડૂકો રમતા ભેળા સાથમાં 
વાતો કરતા થાકતી ના અડધી અડધી રાતના 
એ આજ એના વિના મારે થઇ ગયું અંધારું 
એને એનો જીવ જોણે કોય ના રહ્યું મારું 
હો આજ નથી મારી પાહે મને લાડ કરનાર 
હુકાઇ ગયા શરીર ખોઈ વાલ કરનાર 2
એ જમાનો હતો એ જબરો ને હું કરતોતો એને બહુ પ્યાર 
જતોર્યો જમાનો ને વરસ થઇ જ્યાં બાર 1
એ જે દાડે મને ચડે માથું ન પેટમાં દુખાતું
દવાખાને થી દવા લાવતી જઈને મારા હાટું
એ પ્રેમ ના પોણિ ગોડી મને ખોબલે પિવડાવતી
મારા માથે હાથ એનો હેતે ફેરવતી 
એ તું આવશે કે નહીં મને આવે બહુ વિચાર 
તારા વગર એકલો તડપે તારો પ્યાર 2
એ જમાનો હતો એ જબરો ને હું કરતોતો એને બહુ પ્યાર 
જતોર્યો જમાનો ને વરસ થઇ જ્યાં બાર

snippet.title: 3rd T20I | Highlights | Sri Lanka Tour Of New Zealand | 2nd January 2025
snippet.description:
In the 3rd T20I, Sri Lanka and New Zealand went head-to-head at the Saxton Oval. New Zealand won the toss and asked Sri Lanka to bat first. Sri Lanka posted 218 runs on the board for 5 wickets in their 20 overs. A brilliant 101 runs knock from Kusal Parera helped the Lankans to achieve a huge score. The Kiwis got a decent start and faught tooth and nail to achieve the target but fell short by 7 runs. Rachin Ravindra was the star player from the Kiwis team scoring 69 valuable runs.
.
.

snippet.title: VENKY MAMAs tho #SankranthikiVasthunam Full Video | Venkatesh | Anil Ravipudi | Dilraju
snippet.description:
Watch team #SankranthikiVasthunam surprises Victory #Venkatesh in his iconic getups for a fun filled interaction!!
____________________

Watch the lyrical videos here!

#GodariGattu : https://youtu.be/L8s6qxQJKgk 

#Meenu Song: https://youtu.be/2_Z5L0Qa0k4 

#BlockbusterPongal: https://youtu.be/S8NDIJBbd3Q  
____________________

Sankranthiki Vasthunam is the Hattrick film under the collaboration of Victory #venkateshdaggubati, Hit Machine Director #AnilRavipudi and Blockbuster Producers Dilraju and Shirish. Touted as an extraordinary triangular crime entertainer, revolving around three characters- the protagonist, his ex-girlfriend, and his excellent wife. Produced by Sri Venkateswara Creations on a massive scale.

Meenakshi Chaudhary and Aishwarya Rajesh are the heroines opposite Venkatesh. Music is composed by Bheems Ceciroleo, Cinematography by Sameer Reddy, Production Designing by A S Prakash. 

Grand Release WorldWide On Jan 14, 2025. 

Cast:Venkatesh Daggubati, Meenakshi Chaudhary, Aishwarya Rajesh, Upendra Limaye, Sai Kumar, Naresh, VT Ganesh, Prithviraj, Srinivas Avasarala, Muralidhar Goud, Pammi Sai, Sai Srinivas, Anand Raj, Mahesh Balaraj, Pradeep Kabra, and Chitti etc.,

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: INDIA'S GOT LATENT Bouncer Breaks Character | Dostcast w/ Amin Khan
snippet.description:
Amin Khan is a professional bodyguard and has been a bouncer for 18 years in Mumbai. He was a Maharashtra-level bodybuilder and has provided security to celebrities like Poonam Pandey and Nora Fatehi. He has also acted in movies like Ready with Salman Khan. Currently, he is a bouncer on Samay Raina’s show India’s Got Latent.

In this episode, Vinamre and Amin talk about:

•His early days during his bodybuilding career and the consumption of steroids
•The craziest experiences of being a bouncer, Handling crowds in high-pressure situations
•The process of securing VIPs in different scenarios, How celebrities are in real life
•His experience working with Salman Khan in a movie and Amitabh Bachchan in KBC
•The struggles and challenges faced by bouncers, His experiences in dance bars and clubs

Watch this episode to uncover the real-life story of Andrew Tate of India’s Got Latent.

Timestamps:

00:00 - Introduction
0:50 - Who is Amin Khan?
4:40 - Craziest 'India's Got Latent' episode
7:02 - Why are bouncers rude?
7:58 - Craziest experience of being a bouncer
15:45 - Dangerous club experience
20:30 - Dance bar culture in Mumbai
22:10 - How much does a bouncer earn?
25:17 - Working with Salman Khan and Amitabh Bachchan
28:10 - His life after 'India's Got Talent'
30:00 - Reality of celebrities
36:00 - Samay Raina in real life
38:48 - Problems faced by bouncers
41:08 - Salman Khan and Jackie Shroff in real life
43:07 - Drugs and stag entry in clubs
47:55 - Conclusion

Lyrics:
GouJi raa mangala’aaa….
BoJi raa mangala’aaa …

Aat paat ra pai-poTi
AKkale chaayi paarty
Ellaru koodi aaDana

O’ baari oor-kara naad-kaara

Baindh-avi ningak thaKk-kaara
e’ mangala kadiyath-naad-raa

Nuppath-anji naad…. pannerand-komb ra ….dyaavanele
Yaalamale , pommaale , kodag ee …chaayi-nele

Ee kodhi-ra …yaala-male
e kodhi-ra …yaala-male

Kundh-linD kaati nari kyaama
Bollekall ke chokk’ye pochi choma
Komb kott- valaga-kaara
Urpeeth podi-thatt - baara

Aat paat ra paipoti
Akkale chaayi paarty
Ellaru koodi aadana

O’ baari oor-kara naad-kaara
Baindh-avi ningak thakk-kaara
e’ Mangala kadiyath-naad-raa

Rap lines :
Baalo baalo nangada deva
Deva baalo maadeva
Devi baalo maadevi
Patto baalo sooriya

Kooda baalo channoora
Bhoomi baalo jab’bhoomi
Kanni baalo kaveri

Poliye baa
Poli poliye baa …devaa !

Poliye baa
Poli poliye baa …devaa !

Dhudi kotti paat
Paat ‘k sari aat
Nangake sari saati-ye
Nanga kodavaa

Dhudi kotti paat
Paat ‘k sari aaat
Ulagakkella kaatana
Nanga kodavaa …( 2)

Mandh -maanil koodana
Gurukaara-naana - kodavaame-na …Kondaa-danaa

MangalaaDith bandantha
Bendukellarkoo thaKkara Baindh-avi naa ,

Baindh-avi - ellarkoo thak’kaara
BoL’kaat nee’naad umma’thaat
Kombaat nee’naad kathi’ aat

Komb kott- valaga-kaara
Urpeeth podi-thatt - baara

Aat paat - ra - pai-poti
Akkale chaayi paarty
Ellaru koodi aadana

O’ baari oor-kara naad-kaara
Baindh-avi ningak thakk-kaara
e’ Mangala kadiyath-naad-raa

Idh’ kodavaame
Ide’era kodavaame
Idh’e kodavaame ‘ra
Nanga kodavaa (2)
